---
title: Mild Thai Pork & Veggie Stir-Fry with Toasted Coconut & Crispy Shallots
description: Whip up a Thai meal that'll put a smile on everyone's face with this aromatic, yet mild stir-fry. Our fragrant red curry paste brings an authentic touch minus the heat, while sweet chilli sauce and makrut lime leaves ensure the flavour just keeps on coming!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mild-thai-pork-veggie-stir-fry-97fdb4cc.jpg
